  .mission
    .main-container
      .title.light
        We innovate democracy.
        %br
        We make your daily life and the world more democratic.
      .subtitle2.regular.mg-sm
        Parti Coop is a social cooperative established by a group of democracy activists. We are based in South Korea also our work reaches out overseas. As a society, we now have the tools to innovate democracy through digital technology. We provide toolkits, platforms and communities to help to spread democracy throughout every aspect of our society.
